n players include P1\n\n--- Test 18: Players Not on Team ---\n  PASS: Get not-on-team returns 200\n  PASS: Not-on-team includes P3 (Zed)\n\n--- Test 19: Players by Position and Name ---\n  PASS: Get by position+name returns 200\n  PASS: Position+name returns P1\n\n--- Test 20: Leagues of Player ---\n  PASS: Get leagues of player returns 200\n  PASS: Player P1 is in league L1\n\n--- Test 21: Sports of Player ---\n  PASS: Get sports of player returns 200\n  PASS: Player P1 plays soccer\n\n--- Test 22: 404 for Non-Existent ---\n  PASS: Non-existent player returns 404\n  PASS: Non-existent team returns 404\n  PASS: Non-existent league returns 404\n\n--- Test 23: Delete Operations ---\n  PASS: Drop player not on team returns 200\n  PASS: Drop player from team returns 200\n  PASS: P1 no longer in team after drop\n\n--- Test 24: Delete Team ---\n  PASS: Delete team returns 200\n  PASS: League has 0 teams after delete\n\n--- Test 25: Delete League ---\n  PASS: Delete league returns 200\n  PASS: League is gone after delete\n\n--- Test 26: Delete Player ---\n  PASS: Delete player returns 200\n  PASS: Player is gone after delete\n\n=== Results: 54 passed, 1 failed, 55 total ===","is_error":true,"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01VNGgtj6V1xvSn3jNkRiM4Z"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9a37b03b-5080-41c1-93e0-db6136171128","uuid":"1729bf0c-37b6-435b-a831-949ccb63a0e1"}
