{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01T2giHRNfzp8Ef8xM7k9MR1","type":"tool_result","content":"=== Roster Quarkus Smoke Tests ===\nBase URL: http://localhost:34285\nApplication is ready.\n\n--- Test 1: Create League ---\n  PASS: Create league returns 200\n\n--- Test 2: Get League ---\n  PASS: Get league returns 200\n  PASS: League has correct id\n  PASS: League has correct name\n  PASS: League has correct sport\n\n--- Test 3: Create Team ---\n  PASS: Create team returns 200\n\n--- Test 4: Get Team ---\n  PASS: Get team returns 200\n  PASS: Team has correct id\n  PASS: Team has correct name\n\n--- Test 5: Create Player ---\n  PASS: Create player returns 200\n\n--- Test 6: Get Player ---\n  PASS: Get player returns 200\n  PASS: Player has correct id\n  PASS: Player has correct name\n\n--- Test 7: Add Player to Team ---\n  PASS: Add player to team returns 200\n\n--- Test 8: Get Players of Team ---\n  PASS: Get players of team returns 200\n  PASS: Team has 1 player\n  PASS: Player in team is Alice\n\n--- Test 9: Get Teams of League ---\n  PASS: Get teams of league returns 200\n  PASS: League has 1 team\n\n--- Test 10: Get All Players ---\n  PASS: Get all players returns 200\n  PASS: Has 1 player total\n\n--- Test 11: Query Tests Setup ---\n\n--- Test 12: Players by Position ---\n  PASS: Get by position returns 200\n  PASS: Forward players include P1\n  PASS: Forward players include P3\n\n--- Test 13: Players by Salary Range ---\n  PASS: Get by salary range returns 200\n  PASS: Salary range includes P1 (100000)\n\n--- Test 14: Players by Higher Salary ---\n  PASS: Get by higher salary returns 200\n  PASS: Higher salary than Alice includes Bob\n\n--- Test 15: Players by League ---\n  PASS: Get by league returns 200\n  PASS: League players include P1\n  PASS: League players include P2\n\n--- Test 16: Players by Sport ---\n  PASS: Get by sport returns 200\n  PASS: Soccer players include P1\n\n--- Test 17: Players by City ---\n  PASS: Get by city returns 200\n  PASS: Austin players include P1\n\n--- Test 18: Players Not on Team ---\n  PASS: Get not-on-team returns 200\n  PASS: Not-on-team includes P3 (Zed)\n\n--- Test 19: Players by Position and Name ---\n  PASS: Get by position+name returns 200\n  PASS: Position+name returns P1\n\n--- Test 20: Leagues of Player ---\n  PASS: Get leagues of player returns 200\n  PASS: Player P1 is in league L1\n\n--- Test 21: Sports of Player ---\n  PASS: Get sports of player returns 200\n  PASS: Player P1 plays soccer\n\n--- Test 22: 404 for Non-Existent ---\n  PASS: Non-existent player returns 404\n  PASS: Non-existent team returns 404\n  PASS: Non-existent league returns 404\n\n--- Test 23: Delete Operations ---\n  PASS: Drop player not on team returns 200\n  PASS: Drop player from team returns 200\n  PASS: P1 no longer in team after drop\n\n--- Test 24: Delete Team ---\n  PASS: Delete team returns 200\n  PASS: League has 0 teams after delete\n\n--- Test 25: Delete League ---\n  PASS: Delete league returns 200\n  PASS: League is gone after delete\n\n--- Test 26: Delete Player ---\n  PASS: Delete player returns 200\n  PASS: Player is gone after delete\n\n=== Results: 55 passed, 0 failed, 55 total ===\nAll smoke tests passed!","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9a37b03b-5080-41c1-93e0-db6136171128","uuid":"ca18fdfb-cfa0-4b89-8f92-b66b5c630623"}
